<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>로그인 - 한우리 다이어리</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-start: #f0f4ff;
            --bg-end: #e8f6f3;
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
            --text-primary: #1f2937; /* gray-800 */
            --text-secondary: #6b7280; /* gray-500 */
            --primary: #4f46e5; /* indigo-600 */
            --primary-hover: #4338ca; /* indigo-700 */
            --border: #e5e7eb; /* gray-200 */
            --shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.647);
            --radius: 16px;
        }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen,
                Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Apple Color Emoji',
                'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';
            color: var(--text-primary);
            background: radial-gradient(1200px 800px at 10% 10%, #eef2ff 0%, rgba(238,242,255,0) 60%),
                        radial-gradient(1000px 800px at 90% 20%, #ecfeff 0%, rgba(236,254,255,0) 55%),
                        linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-start), var(--bg-end));
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .main-container {
            width: 100vw;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .login-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 420px;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            padding: 32px;
        }

        .login-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .brand {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 56px;
            height: 56px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #eef2ff;
            color: #3730a3;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .login-title {
            margin: 0 0 6px;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .login-subtitle {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .input-group {
            margin-top: 16px;
        }

        .input-label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151; /* gray-700 */
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .input-control {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 14px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: #fff;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: border-color .15s ease, box-shadow .15s ease;
        }

        .input-control:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #c7d2fe; /* indigo-200 */
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15);
        }

        .helper {
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .actions {
            margin-top: 22px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .remember {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #374151;
        }

        .forgot {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6366f1;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .forgot:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

        .login-button {
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 16px;
            height: 44px;
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 15px;
            letter-spacing: 0.01em;
            transition: transform .05s ease, background-color .15s ease, box-shadow .15s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.25);
        }

        .login-button:hover { background-color: var(--primary-hover); }
        .login-button:active { transform: translateY(1px); }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 18px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .login-container { padding: 24px; }
            .login-title { font-size: 22px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="main-container">
        <div class="login-container">
            <div class="login-header">
                <div class="brand">HW</div>
                <h1 class="login-title">한우리 다이어리</h1>
                <p class="login-subtitle">계정에 로그인하여 서비스를 이용하세요</p>
            </div>

            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="id" class="input-label">아이디</label>
                <input type="text" id="id" class="input-control" placeholder="아이디를 입력하세요">
            </div>

            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="password" class="input-label">비밀번호</label>
                <input type="password" id="password" class="input-control" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력하세요">
            </div>

            <div class="actions">
                <label class="remember"><input type="checkbox" id="remember"> 로그인 유지</label>
                <a class="forgot" href="#" onclick="event.preventDefault(); alert('비밀번호 찾기 기능은 준비 중입니다.');">비밀번호를 잊으셨나요?</a>
            </div>

            <button class="login-button" id="loginBtn" onclick="login()">로그인</button>

            <div class="footer">© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Hanwoori Diary</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
<script>
    function login() {
        let id = document.getElementById('id').value;
        let password = document.getElementById('password').value;
        let remember = document.getElementById('remember').checked;

        let params = {
            id: id,
            password: password,
        };

        fetch('/auth/api/login', {
            method: 'POST',
            headers: {
                'Content-Type': 'application/json',
            },
            body: JSON.stringify(params),
        })
        .then(response => response.json())
        .then(data => {
            if(data.success) {
                if(data.data.userType === 'admin') {
                    alert(data.data[0].userType);
                    // window.location.href = '/admin';
                } else {
                    alert(data.data[0].userType);
                    // window.location.href = '/';
                }
            } else {
                alert(data.message);
            }
        })
        .catch(error => {
            alert('Error:', error);
        });
    }
</script>
</html>